{"about_the_game":"<strong>It all began with a woman who fell from a waterfall, starting a cascade of catastrophic events.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/01.png?t=1698416457\" /><br><strong>Lost Life</strong> is a <strong>first person survival horror game</strong>, <strong>oriented on exploration</strong>.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/02.png?t=1698416457\" /><br>\u25fd <strong><u>Explore</u></strong> <strong>Semi-Open World</strong> , discover hidden places and events.<br><strong>Fighting monsters</strong> is not the main point, although it takes a significant part of the game. <br>Your task is to <strong>observe the world</strong> surrounding you and <strong>search for clues</strong> that lead you throughout the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/08.png?t=1698416457\" /><br>\u25fd <strong><u>Find</u></strong> <strong>collectable items</strong> for <strong>customising your stats</strong> and <strong>unlocking hidden events</strong>.<br>In the game, you may <strong>find various collectable items</strong> that may somehow affect your further game experience. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/05.png?t=1698416457\" /><br>\u25fd <strong><u>Fight</u></strong> a <strong>vast diversity of enemies</strong> using <strong>complex combat system</strong>.<br><strong>Different monsters</strong> have <strong>different abilities and weak points</strong>, keep that in mind when fighting them. Some of them are easier to take down in close combat, while others should definitely be avoided. For now.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/07.png?t=1698416457\" /><br>\u25fd <strong><u>Stealth</u></strong> is an option when it comes to saving your life.<br>There is always an opportunity to <strong>stay unnoticed</strong>, but you should also be aware that different <strong>enemies require different approach</strong>. Sometimes you may find yourself in a position where you have to decide whether it is better to move in the dark or just making as less noise as possible is already enough.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/06.png?t=1698416457\" /><br>\u25fd <strong><u>Travel</u></strong> between <strong>alternative realities</strong> to solve the town's biggest mystery.<br>The <strong>world around you constantly changes</strong>. The further you go, the more it changes, and not for the better. The only option for you left is to <strong>adapt and find the cause of disturbance</strong>, whatever the cost.<br>\u25fd <strong><u>Railgun customisation</u></strong> options.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/04.png?t=1698416457\" /><br><strong>Watch the town reveal its darker side right in front of your eyes.</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Oh, wow! Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2020180/5a00cd2160e5391abcabd0dbce0c79346ff4fb06.jpg"},{"name":"Bunker Island King of the hill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2020180/7cd500b5e1a07b890c893e7b2e7d0894ae26232d.jpg"},{"name":"Phoenix Forest Ranger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2020180/0b87f65b14016d63c6ae356aa99c5cd02c477af3.jpg"},{"name":"DragonPhoenix : Through the Forest and Flames","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2020180/9a4f97c10c559624685a0d69362bd69ce7617fce.jpg"},{"name":"Siren Hills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni